item.title: About
item.description: Hey, I'm Sade Smith. I am an experienced Software Engineer with a degree in Computer Science from Carleton College who is currently working in the Chicagoland area. I specialize in web technologies and am skilled in both back-end and front-end development. As a polyglot programmer, I've worked with many languages; PHP, Python, Ruby on Rails, Elm, Javascript, and Typescript, to name a few, and enjoy learning and using new languages.
